Popular actor Yul Edochie has raised the alarm over death wishes on social media for his family. Yul, who has been in the eyes of the public following the announcement of his second wife and son, expressed fury over the fact that his haters are hell-bent on he living a miserable life. The movie star via a post on his Instagram page on Tuesday said whatever feelings or wishes anyone has towards him and his family were mutual. The furious actor wished his haters and all those praying for his downfall to be consumed by their expectations for him. As for his lover, he prayed they experience trifold love and blessings   Erigga asks about ‘Yahoo’ rulers’ penalty over EFCC’s…     Pretty Mike under fire for mocking Christianity     Debate over Tiwa Savage, Tems as Afrobeat queen heats up   “Just seeing someone happy makes a lot of people angry. Very angry o. Some people are even wishing my family death. I don’t understand. “See me I nor dey for ‘God heal my haters.’ If you love me, my triple love and blessings follow you, if you pray for my downfall, may downfall consume you,” he wrote. ”For those harbouring death wish for his family, the father of five prayed: If my lifestyle wen nor concern you dey pain you, make e pain you well well. If you wish my family death, death shall be your portion. You wish me well, it shall be well with you ten times over. Amen!” He captioned his post: “As you wish me so shall it be for you, 10 times. Tuesday morning motivational quote.